<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입 페이지</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fac4cf;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10%;
            left: 10%;
            width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        header {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 90%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #e97da4;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;

            transition: background-color 0.5s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #e97da4; /* 호버 시 배경색 변경 */
            color: white;
        }

        .signup-form {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 300px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .signup-form h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .signup-form input,
        .signup-form select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dddbdb;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: #767676;
        }
        .signup-form button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #e97da4;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-bottom:20px;
            transition: background-color 0.5s ease;

        }

        .signup-form button:hover {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #e97da4;
        }
        .signup-form .links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signup-form .links a {
            color: #e97da4;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .signup-form .links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        h2{
            color: #e97da4;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="로고" onclick="navigateToMain()" class="logo">
        <script>
            function navigateToMain() {
                window.location.href = "/";
            }
        </script>
        
        <button class="btn" onclick="navigateToLogin()">로그인</button>
        <script>
            function navigateToLogin() {
                window.location.href = "/login";
            }
        </script>
    </header>

    <form class="signup-form" action="/signup/register" method="post">
        <h2>회원가입을 위해 <br> 정보를 입력해주세요.</h2>
        <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="아이디" required>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
        <input type="password" name="password2" placeholder="비밀번호 확인" required>
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="이름" required>
        <select name="gender" required>
            <option value="">성별</option>
            <option value="0">남성</option>
            <option value="1">여성</option>
        </select>
        <input type="number" name="age" placeholder="나이" required min="1" step="1">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="이메일" required>
        <select name="interests" required>
            <option value = "">관심사</option>
            <option value = "0">자기계발</option>
            <option value = "1">여행</option>
            <option value = "2">게임</option>
            <option value = "3">요리</option>
            <option value = "4">건강/의학</option>
            <option value = "5">반려동물</option>
            <option value = "6">영화/드라마</option>
            <option value = "7">문학/책</option> 
            <option value = "8">스포츠</option>
            <option value = "9">스타/연예인</option>
        </select>
        <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
        <div class="links">
            <a href="/signup/login">로그인</a>
            <a href="/signup/deletePage">회원탈퇴</a>
        </div>
    </form>

</body>
</html>
